                "image_caption": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "Fig. 1. Conceptual Drawing of Laterally-Driven Resonant Silicon Accelerometer "
                    }
                ],
                "image_footnote": []
            },
            "bbox": [
                109,
                174,
                460,
                361
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "Using governing equation based on electrostatic stiffness changing effect, output characteristic of the proposed accelerometer is estimated. The simulation result is shown in Fig. 2. "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                81,
                419,
                482,
                479
            ]
        },
        {
