            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "CONCLUSIONS "
                    }
                ],
                "level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                83,
                241,
                210,
                255
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "A differential resonant accelerometer, which utilizes the electrostatic stiffness changing effect of an electrostatic torsional actuator, was proposed and fabricated using  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "<111>"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " single-crystal silicon as the structure material. The mixed-micromachining process was developed using pyrex glass substrate and 40 um-thick single crystal silicon with glass cap for wafer level vacuum packaging. The fabricated accelerometer showed the sensitivity of  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "64\\mathrm{Hz / G}"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " per resonator. The measured bias stability estimated by Allan Variance of accelerometer output showed  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "5.2~\\mathrm{uG}"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": ". Therefore, the developed accelerometer is suitable for navigational application. "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                81,
                260,
                482,
                438
            ]
